env PAGER=cat man timing_report_constraint_use_infinity_slack_for_ unconstrained
Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_report..._unconstrained(25.10)    timing_report..._unconstrained(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_constraint_use_infinity_slack_for_unconstrained

Syntax
       timing_report_constraint_use_infinity_slack_for_unconstrained  {true  |
       false}

       Default: false

       Reports the timing slacks of unconstrained paths through the  DRV  vio-
       lating  pin  as  "INFINITY".  By  default,  the timing slacks of uncon-
       strained paths are reported as * (asterisk).

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

